   inversion motion, is combined with a surface by Martin et al. Both
   surfaces are calculated at the aug-cc-pVTZ/CCSD(T) ab initio level. The
   exact kinetic energy operator is an enlargement of the one used in the
   previous two-dimensional calculations. Eigenvalues are computed
   variationally using successive basis set contractions for some symmetric
   and asymmetric isotopomers of ammonia.},
